# Release v0.5.0

## What's New
- Sprint 5 documentation (user manual, proof of concept, development process, deploy, README)
- Authentication: OAuth fully integrated in frontend, Firebase proxy, CORS policies, Ingress NGINX for auth routes
- BigQuery Writer: migrated to Storage Write API with parallel inserts and proto encoding
- AI Agent: improved prompts (quantity, radius, response rules), Anthropic provider support, geocoding fix, K8s deployment with security hardening
- Frontend: auto-expanding chat textarea, a11y improvements, logout button, AI feature integration
- Kubernetes: monitoring ingress, load testing infrastructure, CPU/RAM pod tuning
- Unit tests for agent (campaign, summarization) and BigQuery Writer (proto encoding, row conversion)
